outputs.output_descr: The project covers the Secretariat of the Operational Unit for Development Assistance (OUDA),established by the Prime Minister Decreee No. 1752, issued in the year 2003, and completes the UNDP assistance provided since the establishment of OUDA, towards its functional, institutional and financial sustainability.

project_descr: Consolidation of the Operational Unit for Development Assistance (OUDA) Secretariat
project_title: Consolidation of Oper.Unit for Dev Assist Secretariat
